description: Kate, largely out of the public eye since Christmas, said she was “looking forward to being back at work and undertaking a few more public engagements in the coming months when I can.”
title: Princess Kate says she has finished cancer chemo treatment

description: One of the deadliest single bombardments of the war left dozens of victims to be buried more than 100 miles from the front lines.
title: In Ukraine’s Poltava, soldier buries a father he thought safe from war

description: Aysenur Eygi was killed at a protest in the West Bank. The closure of West Bank-Jordan land crossings has complicated efforts to repatriate her body.
title: Memorial underway for U.S. activist shot dead in West Bank

description: Aysenur Eygi, a 26-year-old Turkish American, was killed while protesting a Jewish settlement expansion in the West Bank. She graduated from college in June.
title: ‘Gentle, brave, silly’: American killed in West Bank remembered by loved ones

description: Vietnamese authorities said dozens of people were dead or missing due to flooding and landslides after Typhoon Yagi struck the country’s north and unleashed heavy rains.
title: At least 26 dead after Typhoon Yagi makes landfall in Vietnam

description: Sudan’s Darfur region was the scene of a genocide two decades ago. Exclusive videos shared with The Post show the inflamed bigotry behind a new wave of killings.
title: Videos from Sudan’s killing fields reveal ethnic hatred behind massacres

description: Witnesses say the Israel Defense Forces fatally shot Aysenur Eygi, a 26-year-old American volunteer in the West Bank. The IDF said it was “looking into reports that a foreign national was killed as a result of shots fired in the area.”
title: Israeli snipers again face scrutiny after death of civilian
